{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Notification.actions","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/actions","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notifications_API\">Notifications API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification\"><code>Notification</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/Notification\"><code>Notification()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><em><code>actions</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/badge\"><code>badge</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/body\"><code>body</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/data\"><code>data</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/dir\"><code>dir</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/icon\"><code>icon</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/image\"><code>image</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/lang\"><code>lang</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/maxActions\"><code>maxActions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/permission\"><code>permission</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/renotify\"><code>renotify</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/requireInteraction\"><code>requireInteraction</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/silent\"><code>silent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/tag\"><code>tag</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/timestamp\"><code>timestamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/title\"><code>title</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/vibrate\"><code>vibrate</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/requestPermission\"><code>requestPermission()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/click_event\"><code>click</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/show_event\"><code>show</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Web Notifications</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NotificationEvent\"><code>NotificationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>ServiceWorkerGlobalScope.onnotificationclick</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration/getNotifications\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration.getNotifications()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration/showNotification\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration.showNotification()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">secure contexts</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>actions</code></strong> read-only property of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification\"><code>Notification</code></a> interface provides the actions available for users to choose from for interacting with the notification.</p>\n<p>The actions are set using the <code>actions</code> option of the second argument for the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration/showNotification\"><code>showNotification()</code></a> method and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/Notification\"><code>Notification()</code></a> constructor.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> Browsers typically limit the maximum number of actions they will display for a particular notification. Check the static <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/maxActions\"><code>Notification.maxActions</code></a> property to determine the limit.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":false,"content":"<p>A read-only array of actions. Each element in the array is an object with the following members:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>action: A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMString\"><code>DOMString</code></a> identifying a user action to be displayed on the notification.</li>\n  <li>title: A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMString\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing action text to be shown to the user.</li>\n  <li>icon: A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/USVString\"><code>USVString</code></a> containing the URL of an icon to display with the action.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://notifications.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-notification-actions","title":"Notifications API Standard"}],"query":"api.Notification.actions"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Notification.actions","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/actions/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notifications_API/Using_the_Notifications_API\">Using\nthe Notifications API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/maxActions\"><code>Notification.maxActions</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Value","id":"value"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The actions read-only property of the Notification interface provides the actions available for users to choose from for interacting with the notification.","popularity":0.0011,"modified":"2022-02-18T09:26:54.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Notification.actions","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Notification.actions","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Notification.actions","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/notification/actions","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/notification/actions/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/93ae23dec42bba9d71d6f1ed45668d8d26847e9c","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification","title":"Notification"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Notification/actions","title":"Notification.actions"}],"pageTitle":"Notification.actions - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexi